sh: 2: /opt/mongodbtoolchain/v4/bin/python3.9: not found
{noformat}
{panel}
That path appears to come from the Evergreen config [here|https://github.com/mongodb-labs/drivers-atlas-testing/blob/fcd042019bf35afed6c67388ee2587290b2a26d5/.evergreen/config.yml#L686].

